# DPDK Installation Guide

Follow these step-by-step instructions to install DPDK on a Linux system:

## 1. Download DPDK

Visit the [DPDK website](https://www.dpdk.org/) and navigate to the "Downloads" section. Download the latest stable release of DPDK.

## 2. Install Dependencies

### Ubuntu/Debian:

```bash
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install build-essential linux-headers-$(uname -r) libnuma-dev
